just the steps that we're doing

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:39.670
but really understand why
we are doing these steps.

00:00:39.670 --> 00:00:41.720
ANNIE CHOI: By looking at the
confocal microscope,

00:00:41.720 --> 00:00:44.350
we actually know how
the results would

00:00:44.350 --> 00:00:46.540
